        },
        {
            "title": "兗煤澳洲將斥資最高24億美元收購Kestrel煤礦80%股權",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/n9GTemB.8hdZLVEizTWUTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED2F1G7_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 兗煤澳洲有限公司(ASX:YAL)週二表示,將從EMR Capital、Kestrel Coal和Adaro Capital組成的投資集團手中收購Kestrel煤礦80%的權益。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兗煤澳洲是中國國有煤炭巨頭兗礦能源旗下子公司,該公司表示將為這筆股權支付最高24億美元,其中包括18.5億美元的預付現金,以及未來五年內最高5.5億美元的里程碑式付款。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kestrel煤礦位於昆士蘭州鮑文盆地,是澳洲最大的在產地下煤礦。該礦2025年生產了590萬噸煤炭,預計還將繼續開採25年。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dead8f7e-d9bc-3f42-a461-b10c65ad86da-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本三井物產株式會社(TYO:8031)保留剩餘20%的股權。Kestrel的銷售主要面向日本、韓國、印度和東南亞買家。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次收購Kestrel煤礦正值澳中貿易關係有所緩和之際。本週早些時候,有報導稱中國已批准從大型礦商必和必拓購買更多鐵礦石貨物。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%97%E7%85%A4%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%B0%87%E6%96%A5%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%9824%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BCkestrel%E7%85%A4%E7%A4%A680-%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A-070259144.html",
